description: TensorFlow is an end-to-end open-source platform for machine learning. It features a comprehensive and flexible ecosystem of tools, libraries, and community resources, enabling researchers to advance the state-of-the-art in ML and developers to build and deploy ML-powered applications with ease.
title: TensorFlow
